Backlight
---------

You can use the following commands to turn on / turn off the backlight:

* Turn on backlight:
    .. code-block:: bash

        echo 1 > /dev/brightness

* Turn off backlight (screen goes black):
    .. code-block:: bash

        echo 0 > /dev/brightness


.. warning::

  | This product only supports to trun on / trun off the backlight, doesn't support to use PWM to control it.


:pagebreak:`True`
